OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClearest in
OL,6,Fthe north for a time, perhaps leading
OL,7,Fto some fog in places and slight
OL,8,Ffrost. Areas of low cloud should
OL,9,Fotherwise spread and thicken from the
OL,10,Fsouth, giving a little drizzle at
OL,11,Ftimes. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FMurky, with extensive low
OL,14,Fcloud that may bring a little light
OL,15,Frain or drizzle, although some limited
OL,16,Fbrighter intervals may develop later.
OL,17,FMilder than on Saturday for most.
OL,18,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
